+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: revenue DESC NULLS FIRST, tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderdate ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |   Projection: tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_orderkey, sum(tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount) AS revenue, tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderdate, tpch.tpch.orders.o_shippriority                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_orderkey, tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderdate, tpch.tpch.orders.o_shippriority]], aggr=[[sum(tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * (Decimal128(Some(1),20,0) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)) AS sum(tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |       Projection: tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderdate, tpch.tpch.orders.o_shippriority, tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_orderkey, tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |         Inner Join: tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderkey = tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_orderkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |           Projection: tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderkey, tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderdate, tpch.tpch.orders.o_shippriority                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |             Inner Join: tpch.tpch.customer.c_custkey = tpch.tpch.orders.o_custkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |               Projection: tpch.tpch.customer.c_custkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                 Filter: tpch.tpch.customer.c_mktsegment = Utf8("BUILDING")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                   TableScan: tpch.tpch.customer projection=[c_custkey, c_mktsegment], partial_filters=[tpch.tpch.customer.c_mktsegment = Utf8("BUILDING")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |               Filter: tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderdate < Date32("1995-03-15")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                 TableScan: tpch.tpch.orders projection=[o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderdate, o_shippriority], partial_filters=[tpch.tpch.orders.o_orderdate < Date32("1995-03-15")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |           Projection: tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_orderkey, tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
